          "date": "2013-12-01 17:01:59.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3534 mdt: enable cross-MDT rename/link",
        "message": "LU-3534 mdt: enable cross-MDT rename/link\n\n1. Remove those cross-MDT check in mdt_reint_rename and\nmdt_reint_link.\n\n2. send rename request to the MDT where the target is,\nif the target does not exist, send to the MDT where its\nparent is.\n\n3. If buf(xattr) is NULL in osp_md_xattr_set, it means\nto delete the xattr indicated by name.\n\n4. Change sanity 24x to check cross-MDT rename/link.\n\n5. Add few tests in sanity 300 to do rename under striped dir.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3a2b9e5e719b37afb5f44df7624b3e29d74c438c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
